# README
#
# Author: Amy B.
#

PURPOSE
---------------------------
    Copy lines of text associated with a single word keyphrase, 
    to be pasted as a body of text for messaging (i.e. email).
    Messages regard scheduling/follow-ups.

ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
---------------------------
    Short project idea taken from:
        Automate the Boring Stuff with Python
        By Al Sweigart

FILES
---------------------------
    - README:       this file
    - mclip.py:     main program driver.


RUN
---------------------------
    Run with:
        python mclip.py [keyphrase]

    - or with a batch file:

        mclip [keyphrase]


BUGS/Notes
---------------------------
    Currently handles 3 keyphrases (see TEXT in program file)